OL,3,CTwo more admit guilt over their part
OL,4,Cin violent disorder in Sunderland
OL,6,FThey both pleaded guilty to one count
OL,7,Fof violent disorder and have been
OL,8,Fremanded in custody until their
OL,9,Fsentencing at Newcastle Crown Court on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FIt comes after Northumbria Police
OL,13,Fexecuted arrest warrants at addresses
OL,14,Fin Washington on Wednesday following
OL,15,Fintelligence, which included footage
OL,16,Fof Adey during the Sunderland unrest.
