OL,3,CTwo more admit guilt over their part
OL,4,Cin violent disorder in Sunderland
OL,6,FIt showed the 19-year-old standing on
OL,7,Ftop of an upturned vehicle after it
OL,8,Fhad been set alight ` behaviour which
OL,9,FDetective Chief Inspector Graeme Barr
OL,10,Fsaid will not be tolerated.
OL,12,FHe said: "This is a great result for
OL,13,Fall involved ` and will hopefully
OL,14,Ffurther reassure communities that
OL,15,Fwe're taking action.
OL,17,F"The behaviour demonstrated by these
OL,18,Ftwo individuals put a lot of people's
OL,19,Fsafety at risk ` and we simply will
OL,20,Fnot tolerate it.
