OL,3,CTwo more admit guilt over their part
OL,4,Cin violent disorder in Sunderland
OL,6,F"There is no place for this type of
OL,7,Fcriminality in our communities and we
OL,8,Fwill come down hard on anyone who
OL,9,Fcauses such unrest."
OL,11,FHe added: "We'd also like to remind
OL,12,Fpeople to continue sharing with us any
OL,13,Finformation which they think may
OL,14,Fassist our investigations.
OL,16,F"As a Force, we are prepared to use
OL,17,Fevery tactic available to us to ensure
OL,18,Fthose involved have their day in
OL,19,Fcourt."
